Françoise Brion https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fran%C3%A7oise_Brion 0 Françoise Brion (French: [bʁijɔ̃]; born 29 January 1933) is a French film actress. She has appeared in 75 films since 1957. She starred in the 1963 film L'Immortelle, which was entered into the 13th Berlin International Film Festival. She was married to Jacques Doniol-Valcroze.
